--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1. ADMIN
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Purpose: Stores administrative user accounts

Columns:
- Id (int, PRI, AUTO_INCREMENT): Primary key
- AdminRef (varchar(45), UNI): Unique reference ID (UUID)
- UserName (varchar(45)): Admin username
- Email (varchar(45), UNI): Unique email address
- Phone (varchar(45)): Contact phone number
- Password (varchar(45)): Password (deprecated)
- PasswordHash (longtext): Hashed password
- UserType (int, DEFAULT 1): User type identifier
- IsActive (tinyint): Active status flag
- CreatedOn (varchar(45)): Creation timestamp
- UpdatedOn (varchar(45)): Last update timestamp

Statistics: 9 rows, Last updated: 2023-07-05

